title: KOLCHAK THE NIGHT STALKER 05 The Werewolf [retr?tv]
description:
KOLCHAK THE NIGHT STALKER (1974)

5. The Werewolf  11/1/1974 

Carl takes Tony&#039;s place on the final cruise of the Hanover to write a feature story. But when passengers and crew alike are found mauled under the light of the full moon, Carl suspects he&#039;s found a much bigger story - a soldier who survived a wolf attack, only to become a creature of legend - a werewolf.

This was originally released on Demonoid and has been circulating sporadically via DHT. 
I thought it would be good to try to join the swarms together and give it new life. 
I&#039;m sure Kolchak would approve. ;)
